{"tid":1819613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"11/1 想蔡英文贏嘅即刻同我翻屋企!!!","createTime":"2020-01-11T03:14:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-11T12:46:25.000Z","uid":81385,"like":3,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"220acf096172dd46b693c9ac7a952aed056adf58","tid":1819613,"uid":81385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T03:14:18.000Z","msg":"今日藍營媒體同cctvb已經準備好哂影任何活動嘅亂局，包括貼連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n中共會派d藍民搞事，狗會放軟手腳任你打，目的製造畫面幫條魚助選<br />\n<br />\n條魚選到代表台灣統一成功，香港再冇利用價值<br />\n咩美國人權法都幫唔到手<br />\n仲未計會遣返在台手足<br />\n<br />\n總之今日屋企要人<br />\n過左大選你做乜都唔割<br />\n但今日你幫左中共助選，全香港聽日就陪葬"},{"pid":"9c4ded84a431150538d5acb99238f7593e639a15","tid":1819613,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T03:18:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46e9fe9d7a4613e710abe23ce03a94f13cea16a0","tid":1819613,"uid":3853,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T03:22:59.000Z","msg":"你噏乜，台灣人一早將中共暴行同一國兩制嘅失敗睇到晒。人哋今日就投票，要投藍或綠嘅一早就堅定咗信念。人哋投蔡英文係為咗台灣嘅未來同自由民主，唔好下下都以為自己咁重要，真係想蔡英文贏嘅就呼籲認識嘅台灣朋友去投票"},{"pid":"d7b75254a460482589c681fd3d48b18367c35b40","tid":1819613,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T03:23:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n今日第一個<br />\n送頭撚出現<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"f24b1a1e1d5a79e80ed59ad9b87f54188c83e95a","tid":1819613,"uid":210727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T03:23:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9d40f739c0d265f1f93b261d458ef38268c480f2","tid":1819613,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T03:35:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6f9ad5c59075a891fe07c104e537be087f03c41","tid"